dagger.internal.codegen

Class GraphAnalysisLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • dagger.internal.Loader
      • dagger.internal.codegen.GraphAnalysisLoader

  • public final class GraphAnalysisLoader
extends dagger.internal.Loader
    A Binding.Resolver suitable for tool use at build time. The bindings created by this Binding.Resolver have the correct dependency graph, but do not implement Binding.get() or Binding.injectMembers(T) methods. They are only suitable for graph analysis and error detection.
